quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  11,121,"Sano jilani kwa aŵala ŵangakukulupilila: “Panganyani (masengo genu) mwachimpanganyichisye, nombe uwwe tupanganye (mwatupanganyichisye).”"
  11,122,"“Soni jembecheyani, nombe uwwe tukwembecheya.”"
  11,123,"Soni Allah ni Nsyene yakusisika ya kumawunde ni petaka, soni Kukwakwe nikwakuujila ichindu yosope, basi mun’galagatilani ni kwegamila Kukwakwe, sano Ambuje ŵenu nganaŵa ŵanti ningaimanya yankutenda ŵanganyammwe."
  12,82,"“Soni uwusyani musi (wa Misra) watwalijimo, ni nkutula watwaliji nao pakuwuja, soni chisimu uwwe tukuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  12,83,"(Yaakubu) jwatite: “(Ngwamba!) Nambo kuti mitima jenu jinsalalichisye chitendo chinechakwe. Basi (chatindende une) nikupilila kwambone, mwine Allah kuŵa nkwikanao kukwangu wosopeŵene, chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka.”"
  12,84,"Sano jwalakwe jwatundumalile ŵanganyao nijwatite: “Ha, kudandaula kwangune ya Yusufu!” Nigatatele meso gakwe ligongo lyamadandausi, basi nijwaliji jwakusisa nnope (madandausi gakwego)."
  14,28,"Ana nganimwaona aŵala ŵaatindenye ukoto wa Allah ni ukafili, ni kwayikasya ŵandu ŵao (ŵaŵakuyaga payakusakala) ku nyumba ja chonasiko?"
  14,29,"(Jajili) Jahannama; tachijijinjila; kaje kusakala malo gakutamilichika gakwe!"
  14,30,"Ni am’bichile Allah milungu, kuti ŵaasokonesye (ŵandu) kwitala Lyakwe. Jilani: “Sengwani (ni umi wenu wannono wa duniyau), nambo chisimu kwakuwujila kwenu ni ku Moto!”"
  15,1,"Alif-Lâm-Râ.   Aga ni ma Ȃya ga m’Chitabu (cha Qur’an) soni ni Chisoomo chakupikanika.",footnotes:1:Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.
  15,2,"Kakajinji katakaŵe achimakafili (ndema jatakaŵe ku Moto) ali nkulajila kuti bola angaŵe Asilamu (paŵaliji ku duniya)."
  15,3,"Mwalekani agambeje kulya ni kusengwa, ni kwaluyaluya liganichisya (lyakupata yambone kwa Allah), basi taachiika kumanyilila (mbesi ja ukafili wao)."